'''Poltur Virus''' was a flesh-eating virus carried by the [[urnsor'is]] of [[Kashyyyk/Legends|Kashyyyk]] for which there was no known cure. The urnsor'is used venom sacs to inject the virus into their victims.

The [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiees]] of the [[Myyydril]] tribe that fought against the advancing urnsor'is in the [[Myyydril Caverns/Legends|Myyydril Caverns]] often died from the virus or had to cut off the infected [[Limb/Legends|limbs]] and replace them with [[Cybernetics/Legends|cybernetics]]. [[Kivvaaa]] lost her arm when she was infected by the virus.

==Behind the scenes==
The Poltur Virus appeared in the video game ''[[Star Wars Galaxies]]'', a [[Star Wars video games|massively multiplayer online role-playing game]] developed by [[Sony]] Online Entertainment and published by [[LucasArts]], prior to its closure on [[December 15]], 2011.

